1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,510
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,980
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,160
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,400
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,730
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,320
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,610
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,060
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,290
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,710
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,200
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,750
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,170
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:08,077
=No Way! My Bro Is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,077 --> 00:01:11,277
=Episode 2=

19
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,280
♪The♪

20
00:01:13,430 --> 00:01:14,750
♪Boundless♪

21
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:15,360
♪Horizon♪

22
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:15,950
♪Is♪

23
00:01:15,950 --> 00:01:16,920
♪Where♪

24
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:18,030
♪My love♪

25
00:01:18,030 --> 00:01:19,190
♪Lies♪

26
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:21,400
♪At the foot of the rolling hills♪

27
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:24,430
♪The flowers♪

28
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,080
♪Bloom♪

29
00:01:34,470 --> 00:01:35,630
Why do you sing

30
00:01:35,990 --> 00:01:37,110
exactly like my bro,

31
00:01:37,110 --> 00:01:38,400
Xiao Dashuai?

32
00:01:39,430 --> 00:01:40,590
You...

33
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:41,840
You know me?

34
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:43,600
Who are you?

35
00:01:44,590 --> 00:01:46,310
I'm Fei!

36
00:01:46,390 --> 00:01:47,310
Gu Fei?

37
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:48,160
How dare you

38
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,710
disrespect His Majesty!

39
00:01:49,710 --> 00:01:50,160
Guards!

40
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:50,760
Seize him.

41
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:52,240
Back off.

42
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,390
Dismissed.

43
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,120
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

44
00:02:04,030 --> 00:02:04,990
Hurry up!

45
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,160
This is insane!

46
00:02:10,310 --> 00:02:11,200
Bro,

47
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,160
why are you here?

48
00:02:12,630 --> 00:02:14,440
You rascal!

49
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:15,880
You tested me.

50
00:02:16,070 --> 00:02:16,990
Wait.

51
00:02:16,990 --> 00:02:18,400
You threatened me.

52
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,360
I didn't.

53
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,550
You even tried to execute me.

54
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,470
I'm going to kill you.

55
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,720
Hold on.

56
00:02:26,070 --> 00:02:27,160
Let's talk business first.

57
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,560
Go on.

58
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:30,200
Got

59
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:31,310
any cigarettes?

60
00:02:42,790 --> 00:02:45,270
We both got sent back in time.

61
00:02:45,270 --> 00:02:46,360
How come you look so cool?

62
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,720
Not bad yourself.

63
00:02:48,350 --> 00:02:49,760
Way better than that smug face

64
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,750
you used to have.

65
00:02:52,630 --> 00:02:54,280
When I got here three years ago,

66
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,920
I was just a frontier soldier,

67
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:57,640
getting baked by the sun every day.

68
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:02,190
How come you show up

69
00:03:02,230 --> 00:03:03,120
and become the Emperor?

70
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,110
Jealous?

71
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,320
Why you?

72
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:06,240
You know nothing at all.

73
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,430
You were roasting on the frontier,

74
00:03:08,430 --> 00:03:10,240
while I was walking on eggshells
in court.

75
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,710
For three years,

76
00:03:12,710 --> 00:03:15,120
I've played cat and mouse with them,
plotted against them,

77
00:03:15,230 --> 00:03:15,950
and sometimes

78
00:03:15,950 --> 00:03:17,070
acted like a madman

79
00:03:17,070 --> 00:03:18,040
to scare them.

80
00:03:18,070 --> 00:03:20,200
Only then did I manage
to purge some of their spies.

81
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:21,720
There's still more to deal with.

82
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:25,920
Everything's finally in place.

83
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:27,480
After this palace examination,

84
00:03:27,550 --> 00:03:29,390
we'll be able to

85
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:30,870
(Palace)
bring Xiao Ce down.

86
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:33,000
Over the years,

87
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,200
he has rooted out

88
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,480
(Sun Beiming)
every spy we planted

89
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:37,240
(Commander of the Imperial Guards of Jing)
by his side.

90
00:03:38,390 --> 00:03:40,240
Then he has one to blame

91
00:03:40,830 --> 00:03:42,600
when I make my move.

92
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:45,390
Don't worry, General Sun.

93
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:48,160
(Lu Ding, Vice Minister of War of Jing)
Our men have already made their move.

94
00:03:52,070 --> 00:03:53,630
I remember I only traveled through time

95
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:54,760
after I died.

96
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,040
How did you get here?

97
00:03:58,350 --> 00:03:59,390
On graduation day,

98
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:00,990
everyone got drunk.

99
00:04:01,510 --> 00:04:02,870
You fell into the water,

100
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:04,320
and I jumped in to save you.

101
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:05,160
Are you nuts?

102
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,870
You can't swim,
and you jumped in to save me?

103
00:04:07,510 --> 00:04:08,870
I guess I was.

104
00:04:12,110 --> 00:04:14,040
I was drunk.
Maybe I wasn't thinking straight.

105
00:04:14,550 --> 00:04:15,670
But I do think

106
00:04:16,550 --> 00:04:17,830
life here isn't so bad.

107
00:04:17,830 --> 00:04:20,040
I don't have to look for a job
and work like a corporate slave.

108
00:04:20,110 --> 00:04:21,920
I finally get to show what I can do.

109
00:04:22,110 --> 00:04:23,240
Maybe I can become

110
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:25,390
the greatest emperor.

111
00:04:25,790 --> 00:04:27,600
Is that how smart students think?

112
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,830
Now you've got wealth
and beautiful women.

113
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:31,870
Go ahead and enjoy your life.
Isn't that good?

114
00:04:32,510 --> 00:04:33,430
I can't.

115
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:35,110
If I sit on this throne,

116
00:04:35,110 --> 00:04:36,990
I have to shoulder its responsibilities.

117
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:40,320
The treasury is empty.

118
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,360
The court is in turmoil.

119
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:44,480
General Sun commands the army
and is watching my every move.

120
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,920
If I do nothing,

121
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:48,040
you think only the people suffer?

122
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,880
I'd be killed by him in no time.

123
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:50,830
You know?

124
00:04:57,053 --> 00:04:58,280
You died saving me

125
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,280
in our last life.

126
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,160
In this life,

127
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,320
I'll help you.

128
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:05,150
The court is a mess.

129
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:06,950
You should go back to the frontier.

130
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:09,150
My bro's the Emperor.

131
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,510
As long as you keep the throne,

132
00:05:10,510 --> 00:05:12,800
my dream of living an easy life
will be within reach soon.

133
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:15,360
Until everything is under control,

134
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,430
I've got your back.

135
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:21,990
We'll be the strongest

136
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:24,280
political-business duo.

137
00:05:25,110 --> 00:05:27,280
You'll be the Emperor
of the legitimate world.

138
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:29,750
I'll be the Emperor of the underworld.

139
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,430
Your Majesty!

140
00:05:38,990 --> 00:05:40,150
Your Majesty!

141
00:05:40,230 --> 00:05:41,400
Your Majesty!

142
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,670
Your Majesty,

143
00:05:43,670 --> 00:05:45,110
this is bad!

144
00:05:45,110 --> 00:05:46,990
Chancellor Hu is waiting outside.

145
00:05:46,990 --> 00:05:47,870
He says

146
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:50,360
all the officials are rebelling.

147
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,160
What do you mean

148
00:05:57,230 --> 00:05:59,800
by "all the officials are rebelling"?

149
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:01,360
You're saying

150
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,000
that General Sun Beijing

151
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:05,160
took advantage of everyone
being in Taiji Hall for an exam

152
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,670
and kidnapped their families?

153
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:08,120
Yes.

154
00:06:08,430 --> 00:06:11,550
Did anyone know you
entered the palace to meet me?

155
00:06:12,430 --> 00:06:13,510
Your Majesty,

156
00:06:13,540 --> 00:06:15,480
(Hu Wenyuan, Grand Chancellor of Jing)
No one knows about it.

157
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,430
Good.

158
00:06:16,430 --> 00:06:18,550
That puts the enemy in the open
and us in the shadows.

159
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,160
Tomorrow in court,

160
00:06:22,190 --> 00:06:23,550
I'll pretend I know nothing

161
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,430
and stall for some time.

162
00:06:26,670 --> 00:06:27,480
Right now,

163
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,510
we can't openly mobilize troops.

164
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:33,680
Gu Bei.

165
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,600
Take Eunuch Xu
and leave the palace immediately.

166
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:37,750
Find a chance
to rescue the officials' families.

167
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:40,750
Well...

168
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:42,360
I need one more person.

169
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,880
Any leads?

170
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:55,920
The people of the plains

171
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,480
grow up on horseback.

172
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:59,760
Reading hoofprints, catching
a horse's scent, and tracking people

173
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:01,110
are our specialties.

174
00:07:01,350 --> 00:07:04,280
Just now, I followed the trail
from every official's residence.

175
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:05,510
It all leads here.

176
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:06,950
Xu,

177
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:08,020
what place is that?

178
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:11,720
The charity granary outside the city.

179
00:07:13,190 --> 00:07:15,070
It's an open area.

180
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:17,430
Apart from the workers
guarding the granary,

181
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:19,040
hardly anyone goes there.

182
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:21,360
There are very few soldiers
stationed there.

183
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,190
It's a perfect place to hide captives.

184
00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:38,000
General,

185
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:39,430
the officials have learned

186
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:40,960
that their families are missing.

187
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,590
They all understand

188
00:07:42,870 --> 00:07:44,800
that they have to obey you

189
00:07:45,350 --> 00:07:47,670
to keep their families safe.

190
00:08:01,230 --> 00:08:02,960
There aren't many guards,

191
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:04,800
but they're
all General Sun's trusted men.

192
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:06,110
We can't charge in.

193
00:08:06,350 --> 00:08:08,040
Of course not.

194
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,550
We'll need

195
00:08:09,670 --> 00:08:10,830
this.

196
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:15,840
What is this?

197
00:08:20,430 --> 00:08:21,160
Wow.

198
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,320
Amazing.

199
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:25,160
You actually built a bomb?

200
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:27,190
I've survived
countless assassination attempts

201
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:28,160
over the past three years.

202
00:08:28,520 --> 00:08:31,140
If I hadn't made a few hidden weapons,
I'd have been dead long ago.

203
00:08:31,990 --> 00:08:33,720
Watch this.

204
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,750
Mind you.

205
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:38,240
Don't cover your ears.

206
00:08:56,550 --> 00:08:57,800
You stay here.

207
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,310
You're too old,

208
00:08:59,310 --> 00:09:00,870
and you don't know martial arts.

209
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:02,080
Cover our retreat.

210
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,040
Right.

211
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:04,430
You'd only slow us down.

212
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:07,200
But I...

213
00:09:22,550 --> 00:09:23,710
Your Majesty,

214
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:25,840
we have a memorial.

215
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:26,990
Speak.

216
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,720
Guanzhong has suffered
three months of drought.

217
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,340
Meanwhile, the Yellow River
has flooded again.

218
00:09:30,340 --> 00:09:31,750
The Astronomical Bureau...

219
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:32,870
Get to the point.

220
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,280
Efficiency.

221
00:09:36,900 --> 00:09:38,870
Since Your Majesty ascended the throne
six years ago,

222
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:41,600
you have favored the wicked
and alienated the worthy,

223
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:44,000
bringing corruption to the court

224
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,190
and ruin to the laws...

225
00:09:45,190 --> 00:09:46,350
Enough.

226
00:09:46,850 --> 00:09:48,800
Memorizing all that
must've taken a lot of effort.

227
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:50,840
Are you trying

228
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:53,560
to depose me?

229
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,120
Move.

230
00:09:59,120 --> 00:09:59,590
Move.

231
00:09:59,590 --> 00:10:00,750
Hurry.

232
00:10:14,940 --> 00:10:16,800
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

233
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:19,180
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

234
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:24,620
♪The brainy emperor plots the strategy♪

235
00:10:24,620 --> 00:10:29,000
♪The slacker general leads the charge♪

236
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:31,410
♪Swords clash and warhorses thunder♪

237
00:10:31,410 --> 00:10:33,950
♪Let the history judge our deeds♪

238
00:10:33,950 --> 00:10:39,620
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

239
00:10:39,620 --> 00:10:45,180
♪Peace across the land, carefree at last♪

240
00:10:49,470 --> 00:10:51,530
♪Funny moments never stop♪

241
00:10:52,150 --> 00:10:54,340
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

242
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:58,710
♪Yet through every up and down♪

243
00:10:58,710 --> 00:11:00,680
♪We create miracles♪

244
00:11:00,980 --> 00:11:03,440
♪From naive youths♪

245
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:06,180
♪To legendary heroes♪

246
00:11:06,180 --> 00:11:08,130
♪This journey♪

247
00:11:08,130 --> 00:11:12,140
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

248
00:11:12,140 --> 00:11:14,690
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

249
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:20,030
♪Let's create♪

250
00:11:22,070 --> 00:11:29,990
♪A legend of our own♪

